@bartlomieju ProcState is Sync and Send. This means that wrapper should be Arc instead of Rc, but a lot of cloning operations in a single thread. As a result there are 2 options:

1.  Type Flags shoud be renamed to Inner, Create a new type Flags that wraps Rc<Inner>. Inner cloning is used in one place - Proc::build
2. Type Flags shoud be renamed to Inner and Create a new type Flags that wraps Arc<Inner>

